                    <span>I play tennis and I've read the other books mentioned along with this book and the old stand by, "Inner Game of Tennis". <P>This book blows the others AWAY!<P>It is simple to read and easy to follow. I couldn't put this one down the first time through it! I am now going back through it and highlighting all my favorite exercises and examples.<P>The other books are dry and hard to follow. Why go dry if you can have USER FRIENDLY?!?!?<P>This book is better than any book I've read on the mental side of sports INCLUDING those that are sport specific!<P>Buy it and you'll be glad you did.<P>P.S. Write in for the stuff in the back of the book too!</span>
                  
